{
  "id": "6a27d52add17c46eb61e5909",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:大塚英志の物語消費論",
  "created": 1780995404,
  "updated": 1780995458,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a27d52add17c46eb61e5909",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:大塚英志の物語消費論",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995404,
      "updated": 1780995404
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54c00000000007b7ec0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995404,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec1",
      "text": "今日はちょっとオタク文化のお勉強回！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec2",
      "text": "テーマは――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec3",
      "text": "「大塚英志の物語消費論」！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec4",
      "text": "……うん、タイトルだけで急に大学の講義みたいになったな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec6",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec7",
      "text": "大丈夫。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec8",
      "text": "内容自体は意外と身近だよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ec9",
      "text": "アニメやゲームが好きな人なら、一度は経験している話だから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ecb",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ecc",
      "text": "「物語を消費する」という言葉には、どこか不思議な響きがありますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ecd",
      "text": "本を読むことや、物語を味わうこととは少し違うのでしょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ece",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ecf",
      "text": "[** まず「物語消費論」って何？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed1",
      "text": "じゃあまず基本から！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed2",
      "text": "[物語消費論]って何なの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed5",
      "text": "[1989年]に[大塚英志]が『物語消費論』で提唱した考え方。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed6",
      "text": "簡単に言うと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed7",
      "text": "「人々は個々の作品だけでなく、その背後にある大きな世界観や設定を楽しむようになった」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed8",
      "text": "という話。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ed9",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eda",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/物語消費論",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7edb",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/大塚英志",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7edc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7edd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ede",
      "text": "ん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7edf",
      "text": "ちょっと難しいぞ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee1",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee2",
      "text": "たとえば昔話。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee3",
      "text": "『桃太郎』なら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee4",
      "text": "みんな物語そのものを楽しむ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee5",
      "text": "桃から生まれて鬼退治して終わり。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee6",
      "text": "これを単体で味わう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ee9",
      "text": "一冊の本を読み終えるような感覚ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eeb",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eec",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eed",
      "text": "でも近年の作品だと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eee",
      "text": "作品の背後に",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eef",
      "text": " 世界観",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef0",
      "text": " キャラクター設定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef1",
      "text": " 歴史",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef2",
      "text": " 用語集",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef3",
      "text": "みたいな巨大な設定がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef4",
      "text": "ファンはそこも楽しむ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef7",
      "text": "あー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef8",
      "text": "ゲームの設定資料集とか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7ef9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7efa",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7efb",
      "text": "近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7efc",
      "text": "もっと言うと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7efd",
      "text": "設定資料集まで含めて楽しむ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7efe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7eff",
      "text": "[** ビックリマンの例]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f00",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f01",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f02",
      "text": "大塚英志がよく例に出したのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f03",
      "text": "「ビックリマンチョコ」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f04",
      "text": "シールにたくさんキャラがいた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f05",
      "text": "最初は一枚一枚のシールを集める。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f06",
      "text": "でもそのうち、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f07",
      "text": "「このキャラとこのキャラは仲間らしい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f08",
      "text": "「裏にこんな設定がある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f09",
      "text": "という大きな物語が見えてくる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f0b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f0c",
      "text": "あー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f0d",
      "text": "パズルのピースを集めてるうちに全体像が見える感じか！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f0f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f10",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f11",
      "text": "ファンは個々のキャラだけでなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f12",
      "text": "背後にある巨大な物語を楽しみ始める。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f14",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f15",
      "text": "星を一つずつ眺めていたら、やがて星座が見えてくるようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f17",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f18",
      "text": "その例え、めっちゃきれい！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f1a",
      "text": "[** 今のオタク文化にも近い？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f1c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f1d",
      "text": "これって今のアニメにも当てはまりそう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f1e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f1f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f20",
      "text": "かなり当てはまる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f21",
      "text": "たとえば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f22",
      "text": " ガンダム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f23",
      "text": " Fate",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f24",
      "text": " ポケモン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f25",
      "text": " 東方Project",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f26",
      "text": "など。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f27",
      "text": "個別作品も面白い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f28",
      "text": "でも世界観全体を楽しむ人も多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f2a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f2b",
      "text": "わかるわー。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f2c",
      "text": "私もアニメ見終わった後、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f2d",
      "text": "Wiki巡回し始めるもん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f2f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f30",
      "text": "典型的な行動だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f31",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f32",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f33",
      "text": "読書でも似た経験があります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f34",
      "text": "物語を読み終えても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f35",
      "text": "登場人物のその後や世界の歴史を知りたくなることがあります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f37",
      "text": "[** 東浩紀の「データベース消費」との違い]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f39",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f3a",
      "text": "あれ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f3b",
      "text": "前に聞いたことある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f3c",
      "text": "「[データベース消費]」ってやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f3e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f3f",
      "text": "鋭い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f40",
      "text": "[東浩紀]が提唱した考え方だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f41",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f42",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/データベース消費",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f43",
      "text": "物語消費論では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f44",
      "text": "「背後の大きな物語」が重要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f45",
      "text": "データベース消費では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f46",
      "text": "「キャラクター属性」が重要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f48",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f49",
      "text": "属性って？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f4a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f4b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f4c",
      "text": "例えば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f4d",
      "text": " メガネ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f4e",
      "text": " ツインテール",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f4f",
      "text": " クール系",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f50",
      "text": " 妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f51",
      "text": "など。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f52",
      "text": "ファンは物語より、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f53",
      "text": "好きな要素の組み合わせに魅力を感じることがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f55",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f56",
      "text": "なるほど！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f57",
      "text": "物語消費は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f58",
      "text": "「世界観だ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f59",
      "text": "データベース消費は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f5a",
      "text": "「属性だ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f5b",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f5d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f5e",
      "text": "大雑把にはそう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f60",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f61",
      "text": "同じ花を眺めるのでも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f62",
      "text": "庭全体を見るか、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f63",
      "text": "一輪の花を見るか、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f64",
      "text": "という違いにも思えますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f66",
      "text": "[** 物語は終わらなくなった？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f68",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f69",
      "text": "物語消費論から見える面白い点がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f6a",
      "text": "それは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f6b",
      "text": "「作品が終わっても世界が続く」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f6c",
      "text": "ということ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f6e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f6f",
      "text": "あー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f70",
      "text": "続編！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f71",
      "text": "スピンオフ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f72",
      "text": "外伝！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f73",
      "text": "映画化！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f74",
      "text": "ソシャゲ化！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f75",
      "text": "舞台化！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f76",
      "text": "アニメ化！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f77",
      "text": "実写化！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f78",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f79",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f7a",
      "text": "増殖しているね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f7c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f7d",
      "text": "気づいたらラスボスよりコンテンツ展開の方が強い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f7f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f80",
      "text": "世界そのものが巨大化しているからね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f82",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f83",
      "text": "読者や視聴者が、その世界に長く滞在したいと思う気持ちもあるのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f84",
      "text": "お気に入りの街を何度も訪れるように。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f85",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f86",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f87",
      "text": "それめっちゃ分かる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f88",
      "text": "好きな作品って、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f89",
      "text": "終わってほしくないもん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f8a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f8b",
      "text": "[** まとめ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f8c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f8d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f8e",
      "text": "要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f8f",
      "text": "物語消費論",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f90",
      "text": " 個々の作品だけでなく世界観全体を楽しむ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f91",
      "text": " キャラクターや設定がつながっている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f92",
      "text": " ファンは大きな物語を発見する楽しみを持つ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f93",
      "text": " 現代のアニメやゲーム文化にも影響を与えた考え方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f95",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f96",
      "text": "一冊の本を読む楽しみから、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f97",
      "text": "図書館全体を散策する楽しみへと広がった、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f98",
      "text": "そのようなお話に感じました。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f99",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f9a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f9b",
      "text": "なるほどなー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f9c",
      "text": "私もオタクだからよく分かった！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f9d",
      "text": "アニメを見始めたつもりなのに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f9e",
      "text": "気づいたら設定資料集読んで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7f9f",
      "text": "考察動画見て、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa0",
      "text": "関連作品やって、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa1",
      "text": "Wiki巡回してる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa4",
      "text": "それは世界観探索クエストだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa7",
      "text": "いやゲーム扱いするな！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fa9",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7faa",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fac",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fad",
      "text": "でも確かに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fae",
      "text": "好きな作品って「物語を読む」だけじゃなくて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7faf",
      "text": "「その世界で遊ぶ」感じがあるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb0",
      "text": "今日はすごく納得できた！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb3",
      "text": "知識の旅は続く。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb4",
      "text": "物語の向こう側へ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb7",
      "text": "だから急にラスボス前のセリフみたいになるのやめて！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fb9",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fba",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d54d00000000007b7fbb",
      "text": "こうして三人の放課後の談話も、またひとつの物語になったのでした。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995405,
      "updated": 1780995405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d55000000000007b7fbc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995408,
      "updated": 1780995408
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d57e00000000007b7fbf",
      "text": "[ゆるトーク:データベース消費]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995454,
      "updated": 1780995458
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d55000000000007b7fbd",
      "text": "#2026-06-09",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995408,
      "updated": 1780995421
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27d55300000000007b7fbe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1780995411,
      "updated": 1780995411
    }
  ]
}